sqlcode: SELECT DISTINCT Hole_Type FROM tblDHColl WHERE Lease_ID = ? AND Date_Completed >=  ? AND Date_Started <= ? ORDER BY Hole_Type

SELECT DISTINCT m.Drill_Contractor FROM tblDHMetadata m INNER JOIN tblDHColl c ON m.DataSet = c.DataSet and m.Hole_ID = c.Hole_ID WHERE c.Lease_ID = ? AND c.Date_Completed >= ? AND c.Date_Started <= ? ORDER BY m.Drill_Contractor
